HEADER 3 MBHP SHX8 Module

<H1>MIDIbox Hardware Platform, SHX8 Module</H1>

<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="mbhp/mbhp_shx8.jpg" width=600 height=377></CENTER></P>

<P CLASS=INFO>The MBHP_SHX8 module expands <A HREF="mbhp_aout.html">MBHP_AOUT</A> to up to 64 CV outputs. It consists of 8 Sample&Hold chips which multiplex the analog outputs of the MAX525. Please note that this module requires special support from the application which is not possible in all cases. Currently only the <A HREF="midibox64.html">MIDIbox64</A> can drive the module, the worst case latency is 8 mS! In future it is planned to provide also an option for <A HREF="midibox_cv.html">MIDIbox CV</A> with a much less latency, but without the analog input features of MIDIbox64.</P>

