<DL>
  <DT><H2> <IMG SRC="images/bullet.gif" ALT=""> Note </H2></DT>
  <DD>
     <P CLASS=INFO>In order to get the module running, you have to modify the MIDIbox64 setup. Open the main.asm and change following options:<P>
     <PRE><TT>
#define DEFAULT_ENABLE_AOUT 1
#define DEFAULT_NUMBER_AOUTS 8
#define DEFAULT_ENABLE_AMUX 1
     </TT></PRE>
     <P CLASS=INFO>Thereafter rebuild the application like described <A HREF="howto_tools_gpasm.html">here</A>.<P>
  </DD>
</DL>

